Hello and welcome to the Cognitive Progression Analysis Framework (CPAF)! In this book, we will explore the intricate world of cognition, from its foundational elements to advanced cognitive functions. By adopting a systemic approach, we aim to unravel the complexities of cognitive processes and systems, shedding light on how information is processed, deviations occur, and adaptations evolve within the realm of cognition.

